Responsive React Sidebar Navigation
This project demonstrates a fully responsive sidebar navigation built with React. It includes a sidebar with navigation links, icons, and a toggle feature for mobile view. The app leverages react-router-dom for navigation between different pages and react-icons for including icons in the sidebar.

#Features
Responsive Sidebar: The sidebar adapts to various screen sizes.

Navigation Links: Includes links to Dashboard, Products, Categories, Customers, Inventory, Reports, and Settings.

Mobile-First Design: Sidebar is collapsible on smaller screens, providing a user-friendly experience on both desktop and mobile devices.

Icons: Uses react-icons to add visually appealing icons to the sidebar links.

React Router: Implements client-side routing to navigate between pages.
